      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -300,
        -100
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## WA-Appointments-Manager\n\nSub-workflow para gestión completa de citas.\n\n### Ramas\n- **check_availability**: DESACTIVADA (endpoint pendiente)\n- **create**: Buscar paciente → Crear cita en Django\n- **cancel**: Buscar paciente → Buscar cita activa → Obtener token → Cancelar por token público\n- **list_upcoming**: Buscar paciente → Listar citas pendientes/confirmadas\n- **confirm_from_reminder**: Obtener token → Confirmar/Cancelar por token público\n\n### Endpoints Django usados\n- GET /api/patients/?phone={phone}\n- GET /api/appointments/?patient={id}&status=pending,confirmed\n- POST /api/appointments/ (crear cita)\n- GET /api/appointments/{id}/status/ (obtener token)\n- POST /api/public/appointments/{token}/confirm/ (sin auth)\n- POST /api/public/appointments/{token}/cancel/ (sin auth)\n\n### Endpoints pendientes\n- GET /api/v1/appointments/available-slots/?service={id}&date={date}\n- POST /api/agent/errors/ (log errores, ReadOnly)",
        "height": 580,
        "width": 500
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "nota-error-pendiente",
      "name": "Nota - Log Errores Pendiente",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -300,
        1200
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "⚠️ ENDPOINT PENDIENTE: Requiere implementar POST /api/agent/errors/ (escritura) en clinic-app (Django). WorkflowErrorViewSet es ReadOnly. Ver CLAUDE.md sección 5.\n\nAlternativa temporal: log con Set node.",
        "height": 120,
        "width": 480
      }
    }
